  "issue_number": 8568,
  "issue_title": "incorrect treatment of multiple informational HTTP responses",
  "issue_body": "NOTE: this is not the same as <https://github.com/square/okhttp/issues/7440>.\n\nFrom <https://github.com/greenbytes/java-http-1xx-tests>:\n\n~~~\nmvn clean install -Dtest=OkHttpClientTests\n~~~\n\nResponses that contain *multiple* 1xx messages are treated incorrectly:\n\n~~~\n[ERROR] testOkHttpClient104_100(org.greenbytes.http.test1xx.OkHttpClientTests)  Time elapsed: 0.459 s  <<< ERROR!\njava.lang.IllegalStateException: state: 3\n        at org.greenbytes.http.test1xx.OkHttpClientTests.testOkHttpClient(OkHttpClientTests.java:20)\n        at org.greenbytes.http.test1xx.OkHttpClientTests.testOkHttpClient104_100(OkHttpClientTests.java:63)\n\n[ERROR] testOkHttpClient104_2(org.greenbytes.http.test1xx.OkHttpClientTests)  Time elapsed: 0.006 s  <<< ERROR!\njava.lang.IllegalStateException: state: 3\n        at org.greenbytes.http.test1xx.OkHttpClientTests.testOkHttpClient(OkHttpClientTests.java:20)\n        at org.greenbytes.http.test1xx.OkHttpClientTests.testOkHttpClient104_2(OkHttpClientTests.java:58)\n~~~\n",
  "merged_at": "2024-11-05T06:50:55Z",
